description:
Hello, I'm Agatha :)

HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO MEEE 🥳 In this video, I mainly want to share with you my birthday glam tutorial while giving a message to my younger self about makeup. It has been 8 years since I started putting on makeup so why not dedicate a video sharing my thoughts and story of when I first encountered my love for makeup. Enjoy watching don't forget to like and subscribe hihi 

If you do have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them (try ko talaga promise) 

Follow me on instagram @agathaclmn and my makeup portfolio @makeupbyagathaa

Subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching :)

Music used: 
Bullet Train Fantasy (feat Luvbird) - Ibrahim
